teklib/mods/lua/README - Notes about the Lua module

2005-04-30 [tmueller]

This port of Lua (as a fully-featured TEKlib module) requires a patch
and some reorganisation of header files in the source tree.

* unpack the Lua source code distribution here
* apply the patch: patch -p0 < patchfile
* rename the Lua directory (e.g. "lua-5.1-work5") to "lua"
* move the following files to the "include" directory:
  lua/src/lauxlib.h, lua/src/lua.h,
  lua/src/luaconf.h, lua/src/lualib.h
